Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried three times but you didn't wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you must be tired and let you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put on that kind brother act, just try four times from tomorrow on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm digging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gobbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running a marathon in the third period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to eat or I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then. Clean up after you're done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co-op store
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Suguro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't that Okumura? Rare to see you around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to hold on to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I grabbed it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Bon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not kids anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Konekomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grudges about food can go on for seven generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent that we must settle it here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're called Konekomaru? That's one strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're freshmen in the Special Advancement department, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hashino!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nishiwaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oomoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the shop may sell out quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I made you lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our young teacher is popular with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so different even though they're brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Konekomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so familiar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I promised my brother to have lunch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they make lunch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you take it? Such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't eat all three and choosing just one could get really ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this looks so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a school cafeteria and yet there's lobster and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! French, Chinese, Italian... There's everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the True Cross Academy is mostly for rich kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm finally one of the celebs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First we need to buy food tickets from that vending machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! That's one zero too much there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, this is a school for rich kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Screw the celebs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you to the cheapest, 1800 yen A lunch meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the prices of the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To provide first class meals, we buy first class ingredients and hire first class chefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does the cafeteria have to be first class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food is culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiencing first class makes your lives fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says he and then eats instant ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least give me money for living expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I totally forget about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Satan's son has needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a 2000 yen bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious bill, thought to exist only in urban legends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I could buy ten sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fine if I pay that every month on the 10th?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every month? You mean this is for one month?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm supposed to live off that, you dolt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You are dissatisfied? Then how about a 100 yen bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, recently I've been somewhat obsessed with Taisuke Itagaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about your obsession!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The house{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father said it often... "Man does not live by bread alone".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sermons won't fill my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with it? Can you be satisfied with 2000 yen a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I work as a teacher and I get my Exorcist salary as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... There's a way to keep you from starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supermarket Nico-Nico-Hall | Open 24/7 | True Cross Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make lunch for the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I'll save some money and you won't have trouble with lunch, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, cooking is one of the few things you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention guys who can cook are popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? Finally my time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Rin cooks for us he'll wake up in time, and if girls offer me lunch like today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can escape by saying that I brought my own lunch without sounding strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This plan is like taking down two birds with one stone! Or rather, four birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where can I cook? Was there a kitchen in the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could use the dorm kitchen. It's just the two of us in the old dorm anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't have to do it so late in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I make the side dishes the previous night and put them in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you take the cold lunch with you in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll be just the right temperature to eat by lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like common sense for homemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were this good at studying, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your damn business and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, they're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it's this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spotty four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you call me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hungry you are, there are things you're not supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate all the side dishes that I made for today's lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did it? It's just the two of us in this dorm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday at mealtimes our food was prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even think about it, but who cooked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... but who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mephisto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were making our meals every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a temporary replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temporary replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach was the one making your meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it. It's the spirit of the fireplace, if I recall correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sneaks in the kitchen while people sleep and makes meals more delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the correct answer, Mr Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was working here as my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yesterday you used the kitchen and trespassed his territory without permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he became sulky and started boycotting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the reasons, but what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Imp Oatmeal à la Mephisto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny is calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We never even met her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't you dare follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reasons aside, the misbehavior of the familiar is the misbehavior of its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I'll be taking care of your meals until Ukobach recovers his mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will be your cook forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach-smukobach... I don't care. I'll exterminate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beating it up wouldn't help much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this? Everything's cleaned up just as it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cheer up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to work, get lost already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one around who can cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Pheles was with him so I wasn't worried when I left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Sir Pheles! What on earth is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,They had a frantic duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Using all their skills and strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cooking fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They matched the best of their abilities against each other, thus giving birth to a new friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fried rice was damn good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My pork and rice wasn't bad either, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the ultimate lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... He's unbelieveable in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura, is that homemade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Okumura! You're not just good at studying but you're also a great cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my brother made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my brother's really good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, Yukio! Impress them with my cooking skills just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura's brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make such a lunch by yourself, so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus I'll be popular with the girls, for the first time in my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way such a brute could cook at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you teach me how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura's eating his lunch crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been very hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even look, idiocy is contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys who can cook are popular, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just let Yukio take credit for this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The malachites arrived, so I brought you your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you came all this way, how about some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that chick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barging into Okumura's dorm like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's just a maid or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when do you offer tea to a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if we give up here the lunches we made will go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until that chick leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the cook of our dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made this tea as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Thanks, Ukobach!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's so late! I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I have the magic key connecting to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right. I walked all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks, Yuki" she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy if someone says it's delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do? That chick isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be staying in Okumura's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which room is his?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 602.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, someone's been cooking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The side dishes for tomorrow's lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that chick made these?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made octopus wieners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make some fried shrimp too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only deserves this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't even touch the lunches we made...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he eats what that chick cooked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach? Is that you, Ukobach?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ukobach?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to think about it, but I think I know what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He started stewing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're making a stew, you add ginger and a bay leaf to suppress the smell of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your biggest problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's elementary! To think that he forgot it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you trying to make?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach, didn't you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone eats your cooking and says it's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has egg shell pieces in it! Who made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, you don't have to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back, old fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Rin made this omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cook because we want to make someone happy when they eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're happy if someone says that it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I like to cook, why I want to cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would call that thing you're making good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukobach spoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Could it be this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I made it for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to eat it, Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Their chagrin drove Ukobach wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it! Eat the lunches they put their hearts into making!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's nice and salty, and totally delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he ate that huge amount of food alone, without leaving a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Mr Okumura. That's a great countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the girls, they are attending classes today as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Ukobach cheered up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard, just rest for a few more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make you recover fast, Ukobach and I made you this special stamina meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back, dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting scared of food...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.78,0:24:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From next week, we'll be going to a week-long training camp for the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiemi? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Um... Please be friends with me!
