Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.57,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.20,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.75,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:14.71,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:20.00,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:25.13,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:29.89,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:34.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:43.86,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:48.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:53.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:58.71,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
